query:
SELECT 
                s.id, 
                s.name, 
                s.description, 
                s.folder_id, 
                s.created_at,
                COUNT(p.id) as project_count
            FROM 
                series s
            LEFT JOIN 
                projects p ON s.id = p.series_id
            GROUP BY 
                s.id
            ORDER BY 
                s.name
